                        <persName role="scribe" ref="PRS00000">ʾAwsǝbyos</persName>ʾAwsǝbyos (s.
                        Additio 2, <locus target="#6va">6va</locus>)<date>Second half of the 17th
                           cent.</date>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; name of the protagonist and other
                           saints; names of the donors and of the scribe; incipits of Texts I and
                           III, and its subsections (fols. 10va, 12vb, 14rb); incipit of Text II;
                           incipit of Text IV; notes in the upper margin of some fols.; elements of
                           the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.&#xD; On the incipit
                           pages of Texts I, III, IV, V, VI (fols. 3r, 7r, 105r, 116r, 141r), a few
                           lines are rubricated (alternating with black lines)</seg>
                     </handNote>
